        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold m-0 mb-5">When do you need it?</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 grid-cols-1 gap-4">
          <label>
            <span class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[color:var(--text-muted)] mb-1.5">Trip start</span>
